commit.message: Changed VCF files from using the [filename].config.json format to now using the convention [filename].vcf. The readVCF method now parses them using the JSON.parse method, so that they have the same previous behavior. Also renamed existing vcf files accordingly. Also added a page404 method to the server.js class so that we have a standardized way of handling 404s. Also added support for asset requests from paths that are more than one level deep. Also added paths for the video / lesson pages using the new VCF standard.

Fixed an issue with end and start log messages not calling timeStamp properly. Fixed an issue were logLine always added a colon and space, even if stamping was disabled. ALso renamed the timeStamp parameter to stamp, to prevent confusion between that variable and the timeStamp method.
